--><DataType xmlns="http://www.gip.com/xyna/xdev/xfractmod" IsAbstract="false" Label="ConstraintV2" TypeName="ConstraintV2" TypePath="xfmg.tmf.validation" Version="1.8">
   <Meta>
      <IsServiceGroupOnly>false</IsServiceGroupOnly>
   </Meta>
   <Data Label="condition" ReferenceName="JSONPathExpressionV2" ReferencePath="xfmg.tmf.validation" VariableName="condition"/>
   <Data Label="rule" ReferenceName="JSONPathExpressionV2" ReferencePath="xfmg.tmf.validation" VariableName="rule"/>
   <Data Label="name" VariableName="name">
      <Meta>
         <Type>String</Type>
      </Meta>
   </Data>
   <Data IsList="true" Label="dependencies" VariableName="dependencies">
      <Meta>
         <Type>String</Type>
         <Documentation>List of names of other Constraints.

This Constraint will not be checked (i.e. it will be "skipped") if 
1. It contains a dependency to another Constraint (lets call it C) 
AND 
  2.1 The condition of C evaluated to false
  OR
  2.2 C was skipped itself</Documentation>
      </Meta>
   </Data>
   <Data Label="description" VariableName="description">
      <Meta>
         <Type>String</Type>
      </Meta>
   </Data>
</DataType>